<%- include('../partials/head', { pageTitle: '운영자 로그인' }) %>
<div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg w-full max-w-md p-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
      <img src="/img/hansung-logo.png" alt="한성대학교" class="h-14 w-auto" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='inline-block';">
      <span style="display:none" class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-violet-600 text-white text-center leading-[3rem] text-lg font-bold">위</span>
      <div>
        <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg">위원회 자동화 플랫폼</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">위원회 운영 담당자 전용 로그인</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="bg-red-50 text-red-700 text-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-2 mb-4"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if (info === 'registered') { %>
      <div class="bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-800 text-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-2 mb-4">
        ✓ 가입 신청이 완료되었습니다. 시스템 관리자 승인 후 로그인 가능합니다.
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <form method="POST" action="/admin/login" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs text-slate-600 mb-1">아이디</label>
        <input name="username" autocomplete="username" required class="w-full border rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-300 focus:border-indigo-400 outline-none">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-xs text-slate-600 mb-1">비밀번호</label>
        <input name="password" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" required class="w-full border rounded-lg px-3 py-2 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-300 focus:border-indigo-400 outline-none">
      </div>
      <button class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg py-2.5">로그인</button>
    </form>
    <div class="mt-4 text-center">
      <a href="/admin/register" class="text-sm text-indigo-600 hover:underline">처음이신가요? 가입 신청하기 →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
      ※ 일반 위원은 별도 로그인 없이 메일/문자로 받은 링크로 응답할 수 있습니다.<br>
      ※ 데모 계정 (슈퍼관리자): <strong>admin</strong> / <strong>admin1234</strong><br>
      ※ 데모 계정 (운영자): <strong>haksa1</strong> / <strong>demo1234</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
